---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="The Annex">
  <div class="annex-back">
    <a href="/" class="back-link mono-block">← INDEX</a>
  </div>

  <h1 class="sr-only">The Annex</h1>

  <header class="annex-head mono-block">
    <pre class="whitespace-pre-wrap font-[inherit] m-0">From the supplementary materials of the Archive of Bound.
Reconstructor's note: these pages contain documents that did not
fit into the main collection but that I have recovered or
assembled separately.</pre>
  </header>

  <hr class="thin-rule" />

  <article class="prose-column annex-foreword">
    <p>
      These materials are best read <em>after</em> the main archive. They
      contain references to events, persons, and documents that the main
      archive establishes in their own time. Some of them comment on the
      mechanisms by which the archive operates and would substantially
      reduce the experience of first reading if encountered earlier.
    </p>
    <p>
      Some of these materials are also, in the technical sense recognized
      by the relevant authorities, dangerous to a small fraction of their
      readers. I have included them anyway, for reasons given elsewhere.
    </p>
    <p class="annex-attribution">
      &mdash; W. Han, archivist.
    </p>
  </article>

  <hr class="thin-rule" />

  <ol class="annex-list mono-block">
    <li class="annex-row">
      <a href="/annex/timeline" class="annex-link">
        <span class="col-num">I.</span>
        <span class="col-title">A Timeline</span>
        <span class="col-label">historical reconstruction</span>
      </a>
    </li>
    <li class="annex-row">
      <a href="/annex/fragments" class="annex-link">
        <span class="col-num">II.</span>
        <span class="col-title">Fragments</span>
        <span class="col-label">recovered miscellany</span>
      </a>
    </li>
    <li class="annex-row">
      <a href="/annex/quiet-library" class="annex-link">
        <span class="col-num">III.</span>
        <span class="col-title">The Quiet Library</span>
        <span class="col-label">[partial leak]</span>
      </a>
    </li>
  </ol>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .annex-back { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .back-link {
    color: var(--color-faint);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .back-link { color: var(--color-faint-dark); }
  }

  .annex-head {
    color: var(--color-faint);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .annex-head { color: var(--color-faint-dark); }
  }

  .annex-foreword {
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .annex-attribution {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-faint);
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    text-align: right;
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .annex-attribution { color: var(--color-faint-dark); }
  }

  .annex-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .annex-row + .annex-row { margin-top: 0.4rem; }

  .annex-link {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(3rem, auto) 1fr minmax(10rem, auto);
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: baseline;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    color: inherit;
    transition: background-color 100ms ease;
  }
  .annex-link:hover {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .annex-link:hover {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    }
  }

  .col-num { font-weight: 500; opacity: 0.75; }
  .col-title { font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
  .col-label { opacity: 0.65; text-align: right; font-size: 0.8125rem; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .annex-link {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(2.5rem, auto) 1fr;
      grid-template-areas: "num title" ".   label";
      gap: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    }
    .col-num { grid-area: num; }
    .col-title { grid-area: title; }
    .col-label { grid-area: label; font-size: 0.75rem; }
  }
</style>
